File-Format: text/html
Classification-JEL: D71, R31
Keywords: governance, housing, cooperatives

Template-Type: ReDIF-Paper 1.0
Handle: RePEc:btb:wpaper:009
Title: Drug Policy Reform and Integrated Community Support Systems
Author-Name: Duke Johnson
Creation-Date: 2025-08-31
Abstract: Moving beyond prohibition and legalization, this paper explores an 'integrated support' model where economic security (via CCO) and housing security (via PTH) serve as the primary interventions for substance abuse and public health crises.
File-URL: https://bettertobest.github.io/research-hub/papers/pdfs/drug-policy-reform.pdf
File-Format: Application/pdf
File-URL: https://bettertobest.github.io/research-hub/papers/drug-policy-reform.html
File-Format: text/html
Classification-JEL: I18, K42
Keywords: drug policy, public health

