Keywords: development economics, monetary innovation

Template-Type: ReDIF-Paper 1.0
Handle: RePEc:btb:wpaper:013
Title: Corporate Transformation Under CCO-PTF Integration: Reimagining Work Structure in the Age of AI and Automation
Author-Name: Duke Johnson
Creation-Date: 2025-11-22
Abstract: This paper discusses the evolution of the corporation within the CCO-PTF framework. It suggests that as AI automates labor, corporations must transition into PTF-aligned entities where profit is measured in social and environmental impact rather than just Credit accumulation.
File-URL: https://bettertobest.github.io/research-hub/papers/pdfs/corporate-transformation.pdf
File-Format: Application/pdf
File-URL: https://bettertobest.github.io/research-hub/papers/corporate-transformation.html
File-Format: text/html
Classification-JEL: J24, O33
Keywords: automation, labor economics

