Template-Type: ReDIF-Paper 1.0
Handle: RePEc:btb:wpaper:015
Title: PTH Independent Financing Models: From Grassroots Cooperation to Philanthropic Scale
Author-Name: Duke Johnson
Creation-Date: 2025-09-05
Abstract: This paper details financing mechanisms for PTH that do not rely on traditional government debt, including community land trusts, crowd-funding via CCO Credits, and large-scale philanthropic endowments.
