Title: PTH Government Integration: Scaling Through Public Investment
Author-Name: Duke Johnson
Creation-Date: 2025-09-08
Abstract: Complementary to the independent financing paper, this work examines how existing government housing budgets can be pivoted toward the PTH model to achieve rapid, nationwide scale and long-term fiscal sustainability.
